directions: Toss dressing with florets in a bowl.
Lay florets onto a greased cookie sheet or Silpat lined baking sheet.
Bake 30 minutes, toss florets and back another 10 minutes.
Serve topped with fresh parsley and Dean's Buffalo Ranch Dip!
ingredients: ½ cup Homemade Mayo Free Ranch Dressing
title: Oven Fried Ranch Cauliflower Bites with Dean's Buffalo Ranch Dip
